About
-----
Classic snake game written in Haskell. The player controls a long creature - a snake, which roams around on a bordered plane. Pick up food to grow and try 
to avoid hitting the other player or a wall.


Dependencies
------------
sprig - http://code.bluedinosaurs.com/lib/sprig/
        http://hackage.haskell.org/package/Sprig

sdl - http://www.libsdl.org/
      http://hackage.haskell.org/package/SDL-0.6.2


Install
-------
cabal install sdl-image sdl-ttf sdl-gfx sprig
cd /path/to/HSnake
./build.sh
